snippet.title: Lucky Pikinini - Zombie Rampage (PC STEAM Game) | Reveal Gameplay
snippet.description:
Lucky Pikinini - Zombie Rampage is a comic book series getting its own video games, Zombie Rampage 1 comic book will be available to read inside of the game itself. Zombe Rampage has been in production since 24 April 2021. This is early footage.

OFFICIAL WEBSITE: http://luckyPikinini.com
